      <title>拜登呼吁对美国最高法院法官实施新的严格限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/joe-biden-wants-supreme-court-term-limits-changes-on-presidential-immunity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将于周一呼吁立法者通过新的具有约束力的道德规则和最高法院法官的任期限制，这是一项将从根本上改变美国最高法院的全面提案的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/joe-biden-wants-supreme-court-term-limits-changes-on-presidential-immunity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国敦促保持冷静，以色列考虑对戈兰致命袭击作出回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/israel-weighs-response-to-deadly-golan-strike-as-us-urges-calm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在以色列指责总部位于黎巴嫩的真主党发动袭击并造成数名儿童死亡后，美国和其他世界大国试图阻止以色列和真主党的冲突演变为全面战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/israel-weighs-response-to-deadly-golan-strike-as-us-urges-calm</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 07:57:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本有望在十年延迟后实现基本平衡目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/japan-expects-to-hit-primary-balance-goal-after-decade-of-delay</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本预计将在2025年4月开始的一年内实现基本平衡目标，在拖延十多年后终于实现财政健康的长期目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/japan-expects-to-hit-primary-balance-goal-after-decade-of-delay</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 06:04:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>行业组织称停产可能使孟加拉国损失 100 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/shutdowns-may-cost-bangladesh-10-billion-industry-group-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国发生了自总理谢赫·哈西娜在今年一月份选举中延长执政期以来最严重的政治暴力事件，可能给经济造成 100 亿美元的损失，这对于正在寻求增加外汇储备的国家来说是一个重大挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/shutdowns-may-cost-bangladesh-10-billion-industry-group-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 05:20:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯称美国对委内瑞拉选举结果表示严重关切</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/blinken-says-us-has-serious-concerns-on-venezuela-vote-results</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯表示，美国对委内瑞拉选举结果“严重关切”，并呼吁在尼古拉斯·马杜罗再次当选委内瑞拉总统六年后对选举结果进行详细统计。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/blinken-says-us-has-serious-concerns-on-venezuela-vote-results</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 05:04:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰外长西科尔斯基抨击奥尔班在不断升级的争吵中“自私自利”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/poland-s-sikorski-slams-orban-s-selfishness-in-escalating-row</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰外交部长拉多斯瓦夫·西科尔斯基表示，匈牙利领导人在与欧盟伙伴打交道时的“自私”导致该国陷入孤立和衰弱，这是外交裂痕扩大的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/poland-s-sikorski-slams-orban-s-selfishness-in-escalating-row</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 04:18:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉反对派对马杜罗获胜的说法提出异议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/venezuela-election-result-maduro-declared-winner-despite-turnout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗在周日的选举中获胜，反对派否认这一说法并呼吁军方执行其所谓的人民意愿，委内瑞拉的政治紧张局势再度升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/venezuela-election-result-maduro-declared-winner-despite-turnout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 04:10:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行或启动缓慢降息周期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/uk-interest-rates-bank-of-england-may-kick-off-slow-cycle-of-interest-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果英国央行决策者本周首次做出艰难降息决定，该央行可能会警告投资者，不要期待央行会连续降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/uk-interest-rates-bank-of-england-may-kick-off-slow-cycle-of-interest-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉对选举结果保持沉默引起全球担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/venezuela-election-2024-results-pending-hours-after-tense-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉总统选举于周日结束五个多小时后结果仍未公布，此次选举受到广泛关注，对尼古拉斯·马杜罗的权力构成了迄今为止最大的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/venezuela-election-2024-results-pending-hours-after-tense-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 02:11:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉选举开始投票，可能引发重大转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-28/venezuelan-election-could-lead-to-seismic-shift-in-politics-or-give-president-maduro-six-more-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉加拉加斯（美联社）——委内瑞拉反对派在周日的总统选举中获胜，与政府展开对决，此前政府宣布总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗获胜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-28/venezuelan-election-could-lead-to-seismic-shift-in-politics-or-give-president-maduro-six-more-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 04:03:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
